thread.title: DH Sylvanas

author: DH Sylvanas
title: DH Sylvanas
text: I'm not able to raid as I used to after having to deal with a lot of work, so I was happy to see that I could quickly finish Kara in 43 minutes - on the same afternoon that I ordered. The boosters were pleasant and efficient, and we had no trouble what-so-ever clearing the dungeon. Apart from the actual achievement, I did get some great items that I wouldn't have gotten otherwise - thank you for that!
